          "email": "jacques-charles.lafoucriere@cea.fr",
          "date": "2013-01-28 15:15:14.000000000",
          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-1338 hsm: HSM flags feature",
        "message": "LU-1338 hsm: HSM flags feature\n\nThis extends lustre_hsm_attrs struct in MDD to store HSM per-file\ninformation. It adds infrastructure (function, RPCs, ...) to read and\nmodify it, from MDT code or from user-space on clients through llapi\nand lfs command.\n\nThis patch implements:\n- lfs hsm_state\n- lfs hsm_set\n- lfs hsm_clear\n\nmatching llapi functions:\n- llapi_hsm_state_get()\n- llapi_hsm_state_set()\n\nmatching mdt functions:\n- mdt_hsm_state_get()\n- mdt_hsm_state_set()\n\nand MDS RPC:\n- MDS_HSM_STATE_GET\n- MDS_HSM_STATE_SET\n\nSigned-off-by: Aurelien Degremont <aurelien.degremont@cea.fr>\nSigned-off-by: JC Lafoucriere <jacques-charles.lafoucriere@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: Ic8f82ddc9a56206307c2e5be2523fb7ce42b8638\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
